keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map h goBack
map l goForward
map <c-H> previousTab
map <c-L> nextTab
map <c-u><c-u> Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map <c-w> removeTab
map <c-u><c-t> Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map <c-t> createTab
map <c-u><c-g> Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
